{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "72gthno9b5e",
    "category": "movie",
    "source_url": "",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's been on so long, it's starting to turn yellow.",
      "zh": "它放太久了，開始變黃了。",
      "ja": "ずっとつけっぱなしで、黄色くなり始めている。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's not.",
      "zh": "沒有。",
      "ja": "違うよ。",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Whoops.",
      "zh": "哎呀。",
      "ja": "おっと。",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Careful.",
      "zh": "小心。",
      "ja": "気をつけて。",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now you see why it's good to have.",
      "zh": "現在你知道為什麼這樣很好了。",
      "ja": "これがあるといい理由がわかるだろう。",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Relax.",
      "zh": "放輕鬆。",
      "ja": "リラックスして。",
      "time": "00:00:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Why don't you sit at the counter with me?",
      "zh": "你為什麼不坐在吧台跟我一起？",
      "ja": "カウンターに座って一緒にどう？",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why?",
      "zh": "為什麼？",
      "ja": "なぜ？",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The couch is just as easy to clean up.",
      "zh": "沙發一樣好清理。",
      "ja": "ソファも同じくらい掃除しやすいよ。",
      "time": "00:00:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How does school last night?",
      "zh": "昨晚學校怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "昨夜の学校はどうだった？",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's night school.",
      "zh": "是夜校。",
      "ja": "夜間学校だよ。",
      "time": "00:00:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I mean, by the end of the day, I'm not sure much sticks.",
      "zh": "我是說，到一天結束時，我不確定有多少東西記得住。",
      "ja": "つまり、一日の終わりにはあまり覚えていない気がする。",
      "time": "00:00:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And then why bother?",
      "zh": "那為什麼還要努力？",
      "ja": "じゃあ、なぜ頑張るの？",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Your dance career is good.",
      "zh": "你的舞蹈事業很好。",
      "ja": "君のダンスのキャリアはいいよ。",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not suitable enough, according to my family.",
      "zh": "家人說不夠合適。",
      "ja": "家族によると、十分に適していない。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How are things at the hospital?",
      "zh": "醫院那邊怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "病院の様子はどう？",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Anything new?",
      "zh": "有什麼新消息嗎？",
      "ja": "何か新しいことは？",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Same.",
      "zh": "一樣。",
      "ja": "変わりないよ。",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Speaking of, I actually got a run.",
      "zh": "說到這，我得跑了。",
      "ja": "そういえば、もう行かないと。",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm going to be late.",
      "zh": "我會遲到。",
      "ja": "遅れそうだ。",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't forget about my performance tonight.",
      "zh": "別忘了我今晚的表演。",
      "ja": "今夜のパフォーマンスを忘れないで。",
      "time": "00:01:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It starts with seven.",
      "zh": "七點開始。",
      "ja": "7時に始まるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll be there.",
      "zh": "我會去的。",
      "ja": "行くよ。",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good morning, Mr. Sanderson.",
      "zh": "早安，桑德森先生。",
      "ja": "おはよう、サンダーソンさん。",
      "time": "00:01:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You just came for you.",
      "zh": "你只是來看你自己。",
      "ja": "あなたのためだけに来たの？",
      "time": "00:01:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Gorgeous, aren't they?",
      "zh": "很漂亮，不是嗎？",
      "ja": "素敵でしょう？",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What are you people doing about the pain I'm in?",
      "zh": "你們對我這痛苦做了什麼？",
      "ja": "私の痛みについて、みんなは何をしているの？",
      "time": "00:01:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are the doctors just waiting on the test results?",
      "zh": "醫生們只是等檢查結果嗎？",
      "ja": "医者は検査結果を待っているだけ？",
      "time": "00:01:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Which ones?",
      "zh": "哪一項？",
      "ja": "どの検査？",
      "time": "00:01:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I've been poked a dozen times already.",
      "zh": "我已經被扎了十幾次了。",
      "ja": "もう何度も針を刺されたよ。",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll let you know as soon as Dr. Harris back from the lab.",
      "zh": "哈里斯醫生一從實驗室回來我會告訴你。",
      "ja": "ハリス医師が検査室から戻ったらすぐに知らせるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "In the meantime, you can enjoy these beautiful flowers.",
      "zh": "同時，你可以欣賞這些美麗的花。",
      "ja": "その間に、この美しい花を楽しんでください。",
      "time": "00:01:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't like them.",
      "zh": "我不喜歡它們。",
      "ja": "好きじゃない。",
      "time": "00:01:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Out of my way, I have to pee.",
      "zh": "讓開，我要去尿尿。",
      "ja": "どいて、トイレに行かなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:01:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "An admirer, Claire.",
      "zh": "一位崇拜者，克萊爾。",
      "ja": "ファンだよ、クレア。",
      "time": "00:01:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You, Mr. Sanderson, see, doesn't want them.",
      "zh": "你看，桑德森先生不想要。",
      "ja": "サンダーソンさんは欲しくないみたいだね。",
      "time": "00:01:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Older men, huh?",
      "zh": "年長的男人，嗯？",
      "ja": "年上の男性か。",
      "time": "00:01:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You know, you're not supposed to date the patients.",
      "zh": "你知道，你不應該和病人約會。",
      "ja": "患者と付き合っちゃいけないよ。",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll take care of that.",
      "zh": "我會處理的。",
      "ja": "私がなんとかするよ。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks, Jonathan.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，喬納森。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、ジョナサン。",
      "time": "00:01:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No problem.",
      "zh": "沒問題。",
      "ja": "どういたしまして。",
      "time": "00:01:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Has anyone heard from Maria?",
      "zh": "有人聽到瑪麗亞的消息嗎？",
      "ja": "マリアから連絡はあった？",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nope.",
      "zh": "沒有。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:02:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Isn't she supposed to be back from maternity leave on Monday?",
      "zh": "她不是應該週一產假結束回來嗎？",
      "ja": "月曜日に産休から戻るはずじゃなかった？",
      "time": "00:02:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hope so.",
      "zh": "希望如此。",
      "ja": "そう願いたいね。",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you think Maria is really quitting?",
      "zh": "你覺得瑪麗亞真的要辭職嗎？",
      "ja": "マリアは本当に辞めると思う？",
      "time": "00:02:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe the rumors are true.",
      "zh": "也許謠言是真的。",
      "ja": "噂は本当かもしれない。",
      "time": "00:02:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You don't know that, may we talk into?",
      "zh": "你不知道吧，我們去人事部談談？",
      "ja": "それはわからないよ。人事に行ってみる？",
      "time": "00:02:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm going to go make a trip down to HR.",
      "zh": "我要去一趟人事部。",
      "ja": "人事部に行ってくる。",
      "time": "00:02:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You have time to chew.",
      "zh": "你有時間咀嚼。",
      "ja": "噛む時間があるね。",
      "time": "00:02:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You know, if I'm a minute from late back from breakling to make a little federal case, would you solve that hole?",
      "zh": "你知道，如果我從休息回來晚了一分鐘，你會解決那個問題嗎？",
      "ja": "休憩から1分遅れたら問題になるの？",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I mean, I've burned up to a scene with me.",
      "zh": "我是說，我已經忍受了很多。",
      "ja": "つまり、我慢しているんだ。",
      "time": "00:02:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You, anything possible, they've been jumping.",
      "zh": "你，任何可能，他們一直在跳。",
      "ja": "君は何でもできる、彼らは飛び跳ねている。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I mean, humans can swallow something down big.",
      "zh": "我是說，人類能吞下很大的東西。",
      "ja": "人間は大きなものも飲み込める。",
      "time": "00:02:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Humans are capable of a lot.",
      "zh": "人類能做到很多事。",
      "ja": "人間は多くのことができる。",
      "time": "00:02:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Whoa.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "おお。",
      "time": "00:02:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, we got to spit that back out.",
      "zh": "我們得把那吐出來。",
      "ja": "それは吐き出さないと。",
      "time": "00:02:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And then chew it again.",
      "zh": "然後再咀嚼一次。",
      "ja": "そしてもう一度噛む。",
      "time": "00:02:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Who does that?",
      "zh": "誰會這樣做？",
      "ja": "誰がそんなことを？",
      "time": "00:02:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Cows.",
      "zh": "牛。",
      "ja": "牛だよ。",
      "time": "00:02:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I think you'll be my point.",
      "zh": "我想你會是我的觀點。",
      "ja": "君が私のポイントだと思う。",
      "time": "00:02:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You have to enjoy life every now and then.",
      "zh": "你得偶爾享受生活。",
      "ja": "時々は人生を楽しまないとね。",
      "time": "00:02:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I do.",
      "zh": "我有。",
      "ja": "そうだね。",
      "time": "00:02:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So how's your shit going?",
      "zh": "那你的工作怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "仕事はどう？",
      "time": "00:02:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, it's pretty quiet so far.",
      "zh": "哦，到目前為止相當安靜。",
      "ja": "今のところはかなり静かだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I envy you.",
      "zh": "我羨慕你。",
      "ja": "羨ましいよ。",
      "time": "00:02:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Have you tried bribery?",
      "zh": "你試過賄賂嗎？",
      "ja": "賄賂を試した？",
      "time": "00:03:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe Lena will ease up then.",
      "zh": "也許莉娜會放鬆點。",
      "ja": "そうしたらリナも手加減するかも。",
      "time": "00:03:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, she likes to keep me under her thumb.",
      "zh": "不，她喜歡控制我。",
      "ja": "いや、彼女は私を支配したがっている。",
      "time": "00:03:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sometimes I think about quitting.",
      "zh": "有時我想過辭職。",
      "ja": "時々辞めようかと思う。",
      "time": "00:03:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sure.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "そうだね。",
      "time": "00:03:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I even work hard for that nursing degree anyway.",
      "zh": "我還是努力取得護理學位。",
      "ja": "それでも看護の学位を頑張って取っている。",
      "time": "00:03:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm just sorry.",
      "zh": "我只是抱歉。",
      "ja": "ただ、残念だよ。",
      "time": "00:03:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey, you'd miss the patience.",
      "zh": "嘿，你會想念病人的。",
      "ja": "ねえ、患者さんが恋しくなるよ。",
      "time": "00:03:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Better to keep your chin up.",
      "zh": "最好保持樂觀。",
      "ja": "元気を出したほうがいい。",
      "time": "00:03:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All right?",
      "zh": "好嗎？",
      "ja": "いい？",
      "time": "00:03:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Besides, Maria will be back soon, right?",
      "zh": "況且，瑪麗亞很快就會回來，對吧？",
      "ja": "それに、マリアもすぐ戻るよね？",
      "time": "00:03:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不會。",
      "ja": "いや。",
      "time": "00:03:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It feels like the same layout as last time.",
      "zh": "感覺跟上次一樣的安排。",
      "ja": "前回と同じ配置のようだ。",
      "time": "00:03:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So tell Mike, yes, it's not messing with the concept of clean space.",
      "zh": "所以告訴麥克，是的，這不會破壞乾淨空間的概念。",
      "ja": "マイクに言って、そう、清潔な空間のコンセプトを乱さないように。",
      "time": "00:03:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Peyton, she's doing OK.",
      "zh": "佩頓，她還好。",
      "ja": "ペイトンは大丈夫だよ。",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Poor girl's just so tired.",
      "zh": "可憐的女孩只是很累。",
      "ja": "かわいそうに、彼女はとても疲れている。",
      "time": "00:03:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是啊。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:03:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "OK, keep me posted.",
      "zh": "好，隨時告訴我。",
      "ja": "わかった、連絡してね。",
      "time": "00:03:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right, bye.",
      "zh": "好的，再見。",
      "ja": "はい、じゃあね。",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi.",
      "zh": "嗨。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:03:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey.",
      "zh": "嘿。",
      "ja": "やあ。",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey, we're just going to check your vitals.",
      "zh": "嘿，我們要檢查你的生命徵象。",
      "ja": "ねえ、バイタルチェックをするよ。",
      "time": "00:03:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey.",
      "zh": "嘿。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:03:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So I heard you up and decked in me weren't well.",
      "zh": "我聽說你受傷了，不太好。",
      "ja": "君が怪我をしたと聞いたよ。",
      "time": "00:03:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Um, the surgeon said it was pretty messy.",
      "zh": "嗯，外科醫生說情況相當複雜。",
      "ja": "外科医はかなり大変だったと言っていた。",
      "time": "00:03:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's why we're going to keep her on some heavy antibiotics for a while.",
      "zh": "所以我們會讓她服用強力抗生素一段時間。",
      "ja": "だからしばらく強い抗生物質を使うんだ。",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:03:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's Mike.",
      "zh": "是麥克。",
      "ja": "マイクだ。",
      "time": "00:03:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I got to take this.",
      "zh": "我得接電話。",
      "ja": "電話に出なきゃ。",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't be right outside.",
      "zh": "別離開外面。",
      "ja": "外にいてね。",
      "time": "00:03:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "OK.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:04:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hello.",
      "zh": "哈囉。",
      "ja": "もしもし。",
      "time": "00:04:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Uh-huh.",
      "zh": "嗯哼。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:04:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Finally.",
      "zh": "終於。",
      "ja": "やっと。",
      "time": "00:04:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How are you feeling?",
      "zh": "你感覺如何？",
      "ja": "調子はどう？",
      "time": "00:04:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, well, see.",
      "zh": "哦，你看。",
      "ja": "ああ、そうだね。",
      "time": "00:04:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, when the doctor took out your appendix,",
      "zh": "當醫生切除你的闌尾時，",
      "ja": "医者が君の虫垂を取ったとき、",
      "time": "00:04:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "he also had to take out the infection.",
      "zh": "他也必須清除感染。",
      "ja": "感染も取り除かなければならなかった。",
      "time": "00:04:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And then when the appendix burst, the infection spread everywhere.",
      "zh": "然後當闌尾破裂時，感染擴散到處。",
      "ja": "虫垂が破裂したとき、感染が全身に広がった。",
      "time": "00:04:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So it can be a little tricky.",
      "zh": "所以這可能有點棘手。",
      "ja": "だから少し厄介なんだ。",
      "time": "00:04:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Am I going to be OK now?",
      "zh": "我現在會沒事嗎？",
      "ja": "今は大丈夫？",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "會的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:04:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And a few days, you'll feel better.",
      "zh": "幾天後，你會感覺好些。",
      "ja": "数日で良くなるよ。",
      "time": "00:04:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But you just let me know how you're feeling.",
      "zh": "但你要隨時告訴我你的感覺。",
      "ja": "調子がどうか教えてね。",
      "time": "00:04:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "OK, thanks.",
      "zh": "好的，謝謝。",
      "ja": "わかった、ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:04:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you dance?",
      "zh": "你跳舞嗎？",
      "ja": "ダンスをするの？",
      "time": "00:04:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "zh": "哦，是的。",
      "ja": "ああ、うん。",
      "time": "00:04:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My friend's a dancer.",
      "zh": "我朋友是舞者。",
      "ja": "友達はダンサーだよ。",
      "time": "00:04:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm actually going to see your dance tonight at Metropolitan Center.",
      "zh": "我今晚要去大都會中心看你的舞蹈。",
      "ja": "今夜メトロポリタンセンターで君のダンスを見るんだ。",
      "time": "00:04:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Really?",
      "zh": "真的嗎？",
      "ja": "本当？",
      "time": "00:04:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I want to dance there someday.",
      "zh": "我希望有一天能在那裡跳舞。",
      "ja": "いつかそこで踊りたい。",
      "time": "00:04:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, then I'll tell you all about it tomorrow.",
      "zh": "那我明天告訴你所有細節。",
      "ja": "じゃあ明日全部話すよ。",
      "time": "00:04:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "OK.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:04:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There you are.",
      "zh": "你在這裡。",
      "ja": "そこにいたね。",
      "time": "00:04:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The patient in room 412 just threw up.",
      "zh": "412房的病人剛吐了。",
      "ja": "412号室の患者が吐いた。",
      "time": "00:04:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, my shift is over.",
      "zh": "哦，我的班結束了。",
      "ja": "ああ、私のシフトは終わった。",
      "time": "00:04:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I have somewhere to be.",
      "zh": "我有地方要去。",
      "ja": "行くところがあるんだ。",
      "time": "00:04:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wasn't that your patient?",
      "zh": "那不是你的病人嗎？",
      "ja": "あれは君の患者じゃなかった？",
      "time": "00:04:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So, unless you want a bad performance review on your file,",
      "zh": "所以，除非你不想被留下差的表現紀錄，",
      "ja": "だから、悪い評価を受けたくなければ、",
      "time": "00:04:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "you'll go clean it up.",
      "zh": "你得去清理。",
      "ja": "掃除に行きなさい。",
      "time": "00:04:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're quite late.",
      "zh": "你遲到了。",
      "ja": "かなり遅いね。",
      "time": "00:05:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I know, sorry.",
      "zh": "我知道，抱歉。",
      "ja": "わかってる、ごめん。",
      "time": "00:05:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Your seats in the balcony, you can take the elevator over there.",
      "zh": "你的座位在陽台，可以搭那邊的電梯。",
      "ja": "君の席はバルコニーだ。あっちのエレベーターを使って。",
      "time": "00:05:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, that's good.",
      "zh": "那很好。",
      "ja": "それはいいね。",
      "time": "00:05:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Dance for the reception after the performance.",
      "zh": "表演後的招待會有舞蹈。",
      "ja": "公演後のレセプションでダンスがある。",
      "time": "00:05:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I hope I need a mask match.",
      "zh": "我希望我需要口罩配對。",
      "ja": "マスクが必要だといいな。",
      "time": "00:05:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "My friend's one of the dancers and got me a ticket.",
      "zh": "我朋友是舞者之一，給我票。",
      "ja": "友達がダンサーの一人で、チケットをくれた。",
      "time": "00:05:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.",
      "zh": "哇，哇，哇，哇，哇。",
      "ja": "おっと、おっと、おっと、おっと。",
      "time": "00:05:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She's awful.",
      "zh": "她很糟。",
      "ja": "彼女はひどい。",
      "time": "00:05:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She's awful.",
      "zh": "她很糟。",
      "ja": "彼女はひどい。",
      "time": "00:05:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Please don't fall.",
      "zh": "請不要跌倒。",
      "ja": "落ちないで。",
      "time": "00:05:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Please don't fall.",
      "zh": "請不要跌倒。",
      "ja": "落ちないで。",
      "time": "00:05:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It just stopped.",
      "zh": "它剛停了。",
      "ja": "ちょうど止まった。",
      "time": "00:05:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's no big deal.",
      "zh": "沒什麼大不了的。",
      "ja": "大したことないよ。",
      "time": "00:05:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, why aren't the lights turning on?",
      "zh": "那為什麼燈不亮？",
      "ja": "じゃあ、なぜライトがつかないの？",
      "time": "00:05:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's an electrical problem.",
      "zh": "是電力問題。",
      "ja": "電気の問題だ。",
      "time": "00:05:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is it an emergency phone?",
      "zh": "是緊急電話嗎？",
      "ja": "非常電話？",
      "time": "00:05:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, just a button.",
      "zh": "不，只是個按鈕。",
      "ja": "いいえ、ただのボタンだ。",
      "time": "00:05:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Guys.",
      "zh": "大家。",
      "ja": "みんな。",
      "time": "00:05:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, I think I'm going to pass out.",
      "zh": "哦，我覺得我要昏倒了。",
      "ja": "ああ、気を失いそう。",
      "time": "00:05:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm going to know here.",
      "zh": "我快不行了。",
      "ja": "ここで倒れそう。",
      "time": "00:05:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sit down.",
      "zh": "坐下。",
      "ja": "座って。",
      "time": "00:05:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "OK.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:05:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "OK.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:05:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah, I can't breathe.",
      "zh": "啊，我呼吸不了。",
      "ja": "ああ、息ができない。",
      "time": "00:05:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah, we're running out of air.",
      "zh": "啊，我們快沒空氣了。",
      "ja": "ああ、空気がなくなる。",
      "time": "00:05:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, we're not.",
      "zh": "不，我們沒有。",
      "ja": "違うよ、まだある。",
      "time": "00:05:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just breathe.",
      "zh": "只要呼吸。",
      "ja": "ただ呼吸して。",
      "time": "00:05:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you claustrophobic?",
      "zh": "你有幽閉恐懼症嗎？",
      "ja": "閉所恐怖症？",
      "time": "00:05:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "沒有。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:05:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sure.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "そうだよ。",
      "time": "00:05:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "沒有。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:06:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just go down.",
      "zh": "就往下走。",
      "ja": "ただ降りて。",
      "time": "00:06:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Breathe in and out.",
      "zh": "吸氣吐氣。",
      "ja": "息を吸って吐いて。",
      "time": "00:06:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Again, it's OK.",
      "zh": "再一次，沒事的。",
      "ja": "もう一度、大丈夫。",
      "time": "00:06:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's OK.",
      "zh": "沒事的。",
      "ja": "大丈夫。",
      "time": "00:06:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "OK.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:06:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm worried.",
      "zh": "我很擔心。",
      "ja": "心配だ。",
      "time": "00:06:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll get a hold of someone.",
      "zh": "我會聯絡人。",
      "ja": "誰かに連絡する。",
      "time": "00:06:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "OK, it's OK.",
      "zh": "好，沒事的。",
      "ja": "わかった、大丈夫。",
      "time": "00:06:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "On.",
      "zh": "開。",
      "ja": "オン。",
      "time": "00:06:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah, no signal.",
      "zh": "啊，沒訊號。",
      "ja": "ああ、電波がない。",
      "time": "00:06:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, there's.",
      "zh": "哦，有了。",
      "ja": "ああ、ある。",
      "time": "00:06:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:06:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You see?",
      "zh": "你看見了嗎？",
      "ja": "見えた？",
      "time": "00:06:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's a good thing.",
      "zh": "那是好事。",
      "ja": "それはいいことだ。",
      "time": "00:06:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello?",
      "zh": "哈囉？",
      "ja": "もしもし？",
      "time": "00:06:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We're going to be trapped in your forever.",
      "zh": "我們會永遠被困在這裡。",
      "ja": "ずっと閉じ込められるのか？",
      "time": "00:06:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I doubt it.",
      "zh": "我不相信。",
      "ja": "そうは思わない。",
      "time": "00:06:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Someone will come with me first.",
      "zh": "有人會先來救我們。",
      "ja": "誰かがすぐ来るよ。",
      "time": "00:06:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah.",
      "zh": "啊。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:06:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't understand.",
      "zh": "我不懂。",
      "ja": "わからない。",
      "time": "00:06:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Shut.",
      "zh": "閉嘴。",
      "ja": "黙れ。",
      "time": "00:06:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, it sounds like the performance is still going out.",
