      "ja": "公演はまだ続いているみたいだ。",
      "time": "00:06:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're everyone still on the side.",
      "zh": "你們大家還在旁邊。",
      "ja": "みんなまだ側にいる。",
      "time": "00:06:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "See, you know what I'm about to relax.",
      "zh": "看，你知道我要放鬆了。",
      "ja": "ほら、リラックスしよう。",
      "time": "00:06:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, at least we won't go hungry.",
      "zh": "至少我們不會餓肚子。",
      "ja": "少なくとも空腹にはならない。",
      "time": "00:06:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Middle one's worth 100 points, right?",
      "zh": "中間那個值100分，對吧？",
      "ja": "真ん中は100点だよね？",
      "time": "00:06:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yep.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:06:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "OK.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:07:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My turn.",
      "zh": "輪到我了。",
      "ja": "私の番。",
      "time": "00:07:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah, 54.",
      "zh": "啊，54。",
      "ja": "ああ、54。",
      "time": "00:07:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What are you up to now?",
      "zh": "你現在在做什麼？",
      "ja": "今何してるの？",
      "time": "00:07:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "410 to 320.",
      "zh": "410對320。",
      "ja": "410対320。",
      "time": "00:07:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "zh": "抱歉。",
      "ja": "ごめん。",
      "time": "00:07:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nope.",
      "zh": "不行。",
      "ja": "ダメ。",
      "time": "00:07:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can I just use a meatball?",
      "zh": "我可以用肉丸嗎？",
      "ja": "ミートボール使ってもいい？",
      "time": "00:07:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nope.",
      "zh": "不行。",
      "ja": "ダメ。",
      "time": "00:07:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Too easy.",
      "zh": "太簡單了。",
      "ja": "簡単すぎる。",
      "time": "00:07:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Shrimp.",
      "zh": "蝦子。",
      "ja": "エビ。",
      "time": "00:07:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Why not?",
      "zh": "為什麼不？",
      "ja": "なぜダメ？",
      "time": "00:07:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We can say shrimp will work more points.",
      "zh": "我們可以說蝦子得更多分。",
      "ja": "エビはもっと点数になると言おう。",
      "time": "00:07:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're just looking for an easy way to catch up.",
      "zh": "你只是想找簡單的方法追上。",
      "ja": "簡単に追いつこうとしているだけだ。",
      "time": "00:07:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You know, my hands smell like shrimp.",
      "zh": "你知道，我手上有蝦味。",
      "ja": "手がエビの匂いがするよ。",
      "time": "00:07:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, dude.",
      "zh": "是啊，老兄。",
      "ja": "そうだよ、兄弟。",
      "time": "00:07:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The whole elevator smells like shrimp.",
      "zh": "整個電梯都聞起來像蝦。",
      "ja": "エレベーター全体がエビ臭い。",
      "time": "00:07:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here.",
      "zh": "來。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:07:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You.",
      "zh": "你。",
      "ja": "君。",
      "time": "00:07:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So what brought you here tonight?",
      "zh": "那你今晚為什麼來這？",
      "ja": "今夜ここに来た理由は？",
      "time": "00:07:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You dance performance?",
      "zh": "你看舞蹈表演？",
      "ja": "ダンスの公演？",
      "time": "00:07:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah, but why?",
      "zh": "是啊，但為什麼？",
      "ja": "うん、でもなぜ？",
      "time": "00:07:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My friend got me a ticket.",
      "zh": "我朋友給我票。",
      "ja": "友達がチケットをくれた。",
      "time": "00:07:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You?",
      "zh": "你？",
      "ja": "君？",
      "time": "00:07:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I got invited as a work courtesy, I guess.",
      "zh": "我被邀請作為工作禮遇，我想。",
      "ja": "仕事の付き合いで招待されたんだ。",
      "time": "00:07:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My boss got tickets from one of the sponsors.",
      "zh": "我老闆從贊助商那拿票。",
      "ja": "上司がスポンサーからチケットをもらった。",
      "time": "00:07:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I said to get out and stretch my legs.",
      "zh": "我說去外面走走。",
      "ja": "外に出て足を伸ばそうと言った。",
      "time": "00:07:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, I got a back guard.",
      "zh": "嗯，我有背部護具。",
      "ja": "背中のサポーターがある。",
      "time": "00:07:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是啊。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:07:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Switch.",
      "zh": "換。",
      "ja": "交代。",
      "time": "00:07:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I think the performance is over now.",
      "zh": "我想表演結束了。",
      "ja": "公演はもう終わったと思う。",
      "time": "00:07:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hello?",
      "zh": "哈囉？",
      "ja": "もしもし？",
      "time": "00:07:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Someone in there?",
      "zh": "有人在裡面嗎？",
      "ja": "誰かいる？",
      "time": "00:07:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Help?",
      "zh": "救命？",
      "ja": "助けて？",
      "time": "00:08:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Please?",
      "zh": "拜託？",
      "ja": "お願い？",
      "time": "00:08:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We're stuck in here.",
      "zh": "我們被困在這裡。",
      "ja": "閉じ込められている。",
      "time": "00:08:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, hang on.",
      "zh": "哦，等一下。",
      "ja": "ああ、ちょっと待って。",
      "time": "00:08:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Help?",
      "zh": "救命？",
      "ja": "助けて？",
      "time": "00:08:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Please, someone save us.",
      "zh": "拜託，有人救救我們。",
      "ja": "お願い、誰か助けて。",
      "time": "00:08:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How many are in there?",
      "zh": "裡面有幾個人？",
      "ja": "何人いるの？",
      "time": "00:08:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah, three of us.",
      "zh": "啊，我們三個。",
      "ja": "ああ、3人だ。",
      "time": "00:08:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Is everyone OK?",
      "zh": "大家都還好嗎？",
      "ja": "みんな大丈夫？",
      "time": "00:08:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:08:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:08:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We'll get help.",
      "zh": "我們會去救援。",
      "ja": "助けを呼ぶよ。",
      "time": "00:08:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:08:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We're saved.",
      "zh": "我們得救了。",
      "ja": "助かった。",
      "time": "00:08:15"
    }
  ]
}